## Backend / DB rules
- Schema changes go through migrations — no manual DB edits.
- Every new table needs an index on columns used in `WHERE` / `ORDER BY` / `JOIN`.
- No raw SQL strings — use `{{DB_ORM}}` query builder / ORM.
- Paginate every list query; no unbounded `SELECT *`.

